name: Gonzalo Lagos
text:
Excellent place to come.
Very friendly and professional people. I came here two days in a row and was loaded timely  both times.
I will definitely come back here.
Way to go, guys!!

name: j win
text: Friendly and efficient staff. Great customer service.... call ahead, you'll definitely will be granted the very same experience I had.

name: Demetricus Travis
text: Great people around plus I was 2 hours late from leaving my last spot from getting unloaded and they put me to a door as soon as i got there now that what i call a truckers luv

name: Sebastian Kaldwell
text: Always like picking up here. 2 Doors, but plenty of space. They do have appt times, but can really come at any time. Take your phone into the shipping office. The COVID survey is on a website. Set your Reefer to 34 degrees and you'll slide your tandem back.

name: Mark Reiser
text: Easy to load there. Nice people

name: Riri Gang
text: Cannot wait on site while waiting for a dock door. You have to back toward interstate and wait at truck stop..

name: Daniel Bost
text:
Parking is limited. Check in with shipping then told to leave and they will call you to return. Loads are very heavy.. If you have more then 3/8 fuel you will be over 80k gross.

Slow loading with just 2 usable docks. Expect to spend 3 hours here.

name: Mavis Brown
text: They are courteous and  get you in and out  quickly.

name: benjamin cotton
text: Business honored their appointment time for  trucks that are scheduled for pickup when other trucks were waiting. In and out within a hour. Limited truck parking. Small location on busy road.

name: James
text: Awesome place quick on loading .  Trailor needs precooled to 34.

name: marlo dawson
text: Little small for turning a trucking and no parking, clean facility.

name: Harold Hubbell
text: In and out total of one hour
